            <title>[DERBY-3082] DataSourceTest fixture testAllDataSources fails with AssertionFailedError through assertStringFormat on IBM iseries</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3082</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test DataSourcesTest fails as follows on IBM iseries:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) testAllDataSources(org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.jdbcapi.DataSourceTest)junit.framework.AssertionFailedError&lt;br/&gt;
